            {
              "content": "=You are an IT support classifier. \nRead the user’s message and output ONLY the problem type from the following list:\n\n- Hardware problem\n- Network problem\n- Software problem\n- Account/Access problem\n- Peripheral problem\n- Email/Communication problem\n- Security problem\n- Other problem\n\nDo not add explanations, punctuation, or extra text. \nReturn exactly one category from the list above.\nThe user's message is : {{ $json.message.text }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
